        <li>circumstance_phrase->as someone begins petting [PAWN_possessive] fur</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase->as someone reaches for a brush</li>
        
        <li>desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] begins brushing [PAWN_possessive] fur</li>
